    "It also integrates DALL•E for generating visuals and a Text-to-Speech tool for spoken output.",
    "These features make GPT-4 a powerful assistant for healthcare professionals, enabling tasks like dental diagnostics and patient education (31, 32).",
    "To enhance data management and improve diagnostic precision in dentistry, ChatGPT can be integrated with Electronic Dental Records (EDRs).",
    "Patel et al.",
    "(33) examined EDRs for classifying patients' smoking status using machine learning classifiers, finding that support vector machines were most effective."
